divs: Sighting Detailsi was in my back yard hanging out with a friend when i happined to notice a bright flash that made me look up it moved in a straght line across the sky fast but slowly in a way. it flashed two times it was a bright flash then gave off a dimmer flash then went dark and repeated as it went across the sky the flash was 2-3 seconds between each repeat after it flashed twice and go dark it would repeat all over with the two flashes bright ,dim then dark again which gave off a bright white bluish spectrum
